skill.name: Electrocute
skill.description:
This is a Signature spell. Signature spells are free to cast.

Lightning arcs from your fingertips, dealing 138% weapon damage as Lightning. The lightning can jump, hitting up to 2 additional enemies.
skill.simpleDescription:
Signature Spell

Cast chain lightning that electrocutes up to 3 enemies.

rune.name: Surge of Power
rune.description: Gain 1 Arcane Power for each enemy hit.
rune.simpleDescription: Gain Arcane Power for each enemy hit.

skill.name: Arcane Orb
skill.description:
Cost: 30 Arcane Power

Hurl an orb of pure energy that explodes on contact, dealing 381% weapon damage as Arcane to all enemies within 15 yards.
skill.simpleDescription:
Cost: 30 Arcane Power

Cast an orb of pure arcane energy that explodes on contact.

rune.name: Frozen Orb
rune.description: Create an orb of frozen death that shreds an area with ice bolts, dealing 393% weapon damage as Cold.
rune.simpleDescription: Create an orb of frozen death that shreds an area with ice bolts.

skill.name: Black Hole
skill.description:
Cost: 20 Arcane Power
Cooldown: 12 seconds

Conjure a Black Hole at the target location that draws enemies to it and deals 360% weapon damage as Arcane over 2 seconds to all enemies within 15 yards.
skill.simpleDescription:
Cost: 20 Arcane Power
Cooldown: 12 seconds

Conjure a Black Hole that draws enemies to it and deals damage.

rune.name: Absolute Zero
rune.description:
Each enemy hit increases the damage of your Cold spells by 3% for 10 seconds.

Black Hole's damage turns into Cold.
rune.simpleDescription:
Each enemy hit increases the damage of your Cold spells for a short duration.

Black Hole's damage turns into Cold.

skill.name: Archon
skill.description:
Cooldown: 120 seconds

Transform into a being of pure arcane energy for 20 seconds. While in Archon form, your normal abilities are replaced by powerful Archon abilities and your damage, Armor and resistances are increased by 20%.

Each enemy killed while in Archon form increases your damage by 6% for the remaining duration of Archon.
skill.simpleDescription:
Cooldown: 120 seconds

Become a being of pure energy and gain potent new abilities for 20 seconds.

rune.name: Improved Archon
rune.description: Increase the damage of all Archon abilities by 22%.
rune.simpleDescription: Increase the damage of all Archon abilities.

skill.name: Magic Weapon
skill.description:
Cost: 25 Arcane Power

Imbue your weapon with magical energy, granting it 10% increased damage. Lasts 10 minutes.
skill.simpleDescription:
Cost: 25 Arcane Power

Imbue your weapon with magical energy, increasing your weapon's effectiveness.

rune.name: Force Weapon
rune.description: Increase the damage bonus of Magic Weapon to 20% damage and grants a 2% chance to Knockback any enemies hit.
rune.simpleDescription: Increase the damage bonus of Magic Weapon and grants a chance to Knockback enemies.

skill.name: Teleport
skill.description:
Cooldown: 16 seconds

Teleport through the ether to the selected location up to 50 yards away.
skill.simpleDescription:
Cooldown: 16 seconds

Teleport instantly to another location.

rune.name: Wormhole
rune.description: After casting Teleport, there is a 1 second delay before the cooldown begins, allowing you to Teleport again.
rune.simpleDescription: After casting Teleport there is a small delay before the cooldown begins, allowing you to Teleport again.

skill.name: Dominance
skill.description:
Killing an enemy grants a shield that absorbs 12379 damage for 3 seconds. This effect can stack up to 10 times.

Refreshing Dominance will set the shield to its maximum possible potency and each stack will increase its total duration by 0.5 seconds.
skill.flavor: "Why waste your own energy? Using your enemy's to protect yourself strengthens you while it weakens him. What could be more perfect?" â€”Ennead Sage Resko

skill.name: Astral Presence
skill.description: Increase your maximum Arcane Power by 20 and Arcane Power regeneration by 2 per second.
skill.flavor: "Feel the power in the veil that surrounds usâ€”a thunder cloud ready to burst... a volcano about to erupt. Harness it, and you will be invincible." â€”Adria

skill.name: Paralysis
skill.description: Lightning spells have a 15% chance to Stun all targets hit for 1.5 seconds.
skill.flavor: "Some people are shocked by my mastery of magic." â€”Larra Stormlash

skill.name: Prodigy
skill.description:
When you cast a Signature spell, you gain 5 Arcane Power.

The following skills are Signature spells:
 Magic Missile
 Shock Pulse
 Spectral Blade
 Electrocute
skill.flavor: "Heavy steel armor may turn aside a blade, but let's see how well it works against lightning!" â€”Larra Stormlash's infamous faux pas at the Royal Westmarch Joust

skill.name: Intervene
skill.description:
Cooldown: 10 seconds

Taunt enemies within 10 yards of you for 3 seconds when you are hit.
skill.simpleDescription:
Cooldown: 10 seconds

Taunt enemies near you when you are hit.

skill.name: Intimidate
skill.description: Enemies that hit or are hit by the Templar are slowed by 80% for 3 seconds.
skill.simpleDescription: Enemies that hit or are hit by the Templar are slowed.

skill.name: Charge
skill.description:
Cooldown: 10 seconds

Charges a target, dealing 280% weapon damage and stunning all enemies within 8 yards for 3 seconds.
skill.simpleDescription:
Cooldown: 10 seconds

Charges an enemy, dealing damage and stunning nearby enemies.

skill.name: Inspire
skill.description:
Increases your resource generation.

Mana: 7 per second.
Hatred: 1 per second.
Wrath: 1.8 per second.
Arcane Power: 1.4 per second.
Fury: 10% generated.
Spirit: 10% generated.
